CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper December 29, 1951, pg. 13, reads: "Budding Artist - A Promising Art Student and Her Work... Bottom left: The artist at work. Those pictures in the background are all her own... - Harris Photos."
TitMainTitle: Peggy Owens (Skillen) wearing light colored smock and painting, surrounded by paintings in art studio, Carnegie Tech (Carnegie Mellon University)
